messages.message: Of course! How's your day going?
Super. Been interviewing and I have a project proposal to write later. How about yourself?
Just returned after a week out of the office. A lot to catch up on!
Not new, I want to say 3 years old at this point.
It's where our Customer service is based.
Cool.  I thought I saw a bunch of construction in Old Town Scottsdale, any use for a techie like me?  I am on the job hunt.
How are your backend PHP chops? Our tech stack is JS, CSS, html, PHP, MySQL.
I've been using those for 8+ years. I can do back end. Any specific framework?

That's great. I wanted to double check as I believe I saw you applied for a Front end role here and this would easily be full-stack (maybe even focused a little bit on the backend....I'm unsure still). We've been known to use Laravel from what I understand. Is there a time tomorrow or Friday you could possible chat for 20-30 minutes?
Let's do 3 pm. Best number to reach you with (I'm sure I have it in the system...but doesn't hurt to confirm)?
Yeah Arizona time I think it's the same now. DST is weird here.
